当地一家报纸报道称，一名菲律宾海军中将已与北京达成协议，以缓和南海紧张局势，菲律宾军方领导人周三指责中国“恶意影响”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 15:02:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-chief-accuses-china-malign-influence-effort-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯首席执行官反对对华贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-speaks-against-restrictions-trade-with-china-2024-05-08/</link><description>梅赛德斯-奔驰首席执行官奥拉·卡林纽斯周三表示反对对中国实施贸易限制，并强调中国仍然是该集团最重要的市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 13:22:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-speaks-against-restrictions-trade-with-china-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯否认其阻止美国工厂工会组织的说法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-rejects-claims-it-prevented-unionising-us-plant-2024-05-08/</link><description>德国高端汽车制造商梅赛德斯-奔驰周三否认了其一直试图阻止其阿拉巴马工厂组建工会的说法，该工厂将于下周进行关键投票。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 13:01:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-rejects-claims-it-prevented-unionising-us-plant-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>英特尔、高通表示，由于北京方面的反对，对华出口受阻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-flags-revenue-hit-us-revokes-certain-export-licenses-chinese-customer-2024-05-08/</link><description>英特尔周三表示，在美国吊销该芯片制造商对中国客户的部分出口许可证后，该公司的销售额将受到打击，北京方面抱怨此举以国家安全的名义太过分了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 12:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-flags-revenue-hit-us-revokes-certain-export-licenses-chinese-customer-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>解说：壳牌出售新加坡炼油厂及其市场意义</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shells-singapore-refinery-sale-its-market-significance-2024-05-08/</link><description>石油巨头壳牌周三表示，已同意将其位于新加坡的 Bukom 炼油厂（世界上最大的炼油和贸易中心之一）出售给印度尼西亚化学品公司 PT Chandra Asri 和全球贸易公司 Glencore 的合资企业，最终完成了这一进程：去年开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shells-singapore-refinery-sale-its-market-significance-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>降价后苹果iPhone中国3月出货量反弹12%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-shipments-china-rebound-with-12-surge-march-after-price-cuts-2024-05-08/</link><description>中国政府下属的一家研究公司的数据显示，在该公司及其零售商降低价格后，苹果公司 3 月份在中国的 iPhone 出货量增长了 12%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-shipments-china-rebound-with-12-surge-march-after-price-cuts-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>在太平洋地区与中国争夺影响力之际，澳大利亚向台湾盟友图瓦卢增加资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-boosts-funds-taiwan-ally-tuvalu-amid-pacific-contest-influence-with-2024-05-08/</link><description>澳大利亚将把对图瓦卢这个面临海平面上升风险的太平洋岛国的财政援助增加四倍，以巩固一项具有里程碑意义的气候移民和安全协议，同时中国也在向小岛国示好。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-boosts-funds-taiwan-ally-tuvalu-amid-pacific-contest-influence-with-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟冯德莱恩：必须阻止中国充斥电动汽车市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-von-der-leyen-china-must-be-stopped-flooding-ev-market-2024-05-08/</link><description>欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩周三在柏林表示，欧洲需要防止中国向欧盟市场提供大量补贴的电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:23:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-von-der-leyen-china-must-be-stopped-flooding-ev-market-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>德国汽车老板警告称，欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税可能会适得其反</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-could-backfire-hobble-green-deal-bmw-ceo-says-2024-05-08/</link><description>宝马和大众的高管周三警告不要对中国汽车制造商的电动汽车征收欧盟进口关税，称这可能会颠覆欧盟的绿色协议计划，并损害进口中国制造汽车的汽车制造商。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:21:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-could-backfire-hobble-green-deal-bmw-ceo-says-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>韩国欢迎美国决定在电动汽车中扩大使用中国石墨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korea-welcomes-us-decision-extend-use-chinese-graphite-evs-2024-05-08/</link><description>周三，韩国欢迎美国决定将汽车制造商对含有中国石墨的汽车的电动汽车税收抵免资格延长至 2026 年。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:16:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korea-welcomes-us-decision-extend-use-chinese-graphite-evs-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：瑞典减产、石油滑坡，股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-05-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-05-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国着眼于限制中国使用 ChatGPT 等应用程序背后的人工智能软件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-eyes-curbs-chinas-access-ai-software-behind-apps-like-chatgpt-2024-05-08/</link><description>消息人士称，拜登政府准备开辟一条新战线，努力保护美国人工智能免受中国和俄罗斯的侵害，初步计划在最先进的人工智能模型（ChatGPT 等人工智能系统的核心软件）周围设置护栏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-eyes-curbs-chinas-access-ai-software-behind-apps-like-chatgpt-2024-05-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>